       a.fechafac ='7/16/2019' AND   a.cod_subgrupo = 'CONSULTA' and  a.statfact=3  and d.desTipoTargeta is  not null and a.usuario='BORTIZ' 
       GROUP BY  
       desTipoTargeta  
       Order by 
       desTipoTargeta
